 barbaric crime and made to face the full weight of the law”.  Vanguard News Nigeria Mr Philip Shekwo, Chairman of the Nasarawa State chapter of the All Progressives Congress (APC), on Sunday said that President Muhammadu Buhari was sent by God to save Nigeria from total collapse. August 12, 2018 In "News" The All Progressives Congress (APC) in Nasarawa State has inaugurated a seven-man reconciliation committee to broker peace and unity among members of the party. June 16, 2014 In "News" Mr Philip Tatari-Shekwo, the Chairman of All Progressives Congress (APC) in Nasarawa State, has called on the residents to come out en-masse and welcome President Muhammadu Buhari during his state visit. February 4, 2018 In "News"